OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781518689
OL,3,CLewis Hamilton secures first Grand
OL,4,CPrix win for Ferrari in Barcelona
OL,6,FLewis Hamilton claimed his first win
OL,7,Ffor Ferrari with a stunning victory at
OL,8,Fthe Barcelona-Catalunya Grand Prix as
OL,9,Ftitle leader Kimi Antonelli suffered a
OL,10,Flate retirement.
OL,12,FHamilton delivered a brilliant drive
OL,13,Fto nail a three-stop strategy and
OL,14,Fcapitalised on a perfectly-timed
OL,15,Fvirtual safety car to earn his first
OL,16,Fwin since the Belgian Grand Prix in
OL,17,F2024 ` 40 races and 686 days ago.
OL,19,FIn doing so, the 41-year-old became
OL,20,Fthe oldest Formula One race winner
OL,21,Fsince Jack Brabham in 1970.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
