FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781518689
OL,3,CLewis Hamilton secures first Grand
OL,4,CPrix win for Ferrari in Barcelona
OL,6,FHamilton roared into the championship
OL,7,Frace as runaway leader Antonelli `
OL,8,Fwhose five-race winning streak was
OL,9,Fsnapped ` suffered a late engine
OL,10,Ffailure having just overtaken team-
OL,11,Fmate George Russell for second.
OL,13,FHamilton vowed after securing back-to-
OL,14,Fback second places in Monaco last
OL,15,Fweekend that he would chase down
OL,16,FAntonelli and the Italian's lead was
OL,17,Fslashed from 66 points to 41.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781518689
OL,3,CLewis Hamilton secures first Grand
OL,4,CPrix win for Ferrari in Barcelona
OL,6,FRussell had looked on course to secure
OL,7,Fa first win since the opening weekend
OL,8,Fbut Hamilton closed in during his
OL,9,Fthird stint before a cheap pit stop
OL,10,Funder the virtual safety car was the
OL,11,Fgift he needed to end his wait for
OL,12,Fvictory.
OL,14,FIt was a first Ferrari win since
OL,15,FCarlos Sainz's success in Mexico City
OL,16,Fin 2024. Lando Norris finished third
OL,17,Fto seal the first all-British podium
OL,18,Fsince 1968, ahead of Max Verstappen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781518689
OL,3,CLewis Hamilton secures first Grand
OL,4,CPrix win for Ferrari in Barcelona
OL,6,FIt was a baking-hot grid, with a track
OL,7,Ftemperature of 50C at lights out,
OL,8,Fprompting race teams to form their own
OL,9,Fstrategies.
OL,11,FHamilton gambled by starting on soft
OL,12,Ftyres from second, after securing his
OL,13,Fbest qualifying result as a Scuderia
OL,14,Fdriver on Saturday.
OL,16,FIt could have given him the edge off
OL,17,Fthe line but Russell held the seven-
OL,18,Ftime world champion at bay on the
OL,19,Flengthy 598-metre dash down to turn
OL,20,Fone, with Antonelli fending off the
OL,21,Fchallenge of Norris to hold third.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781518689
OL,3,CLewis Hamilton secures first Grand
OL,4,CPrix win for Ferrari in Barcelona
OL,6,FRussell opened up a commanding
OL,7,Fadvantage. Hamilton pitted early on
OL,8,Flap 12 of 66 and Mercedes reacted by
OL,9,Fpitting Russell the following lap,
OL,10,Fboth taking hard tyres.
OL,12,FNorris also came in but now race
OL,13,Fleader Antonelli stayed out. Russell
OL,14,Fwas nervous, telling his engineer:
OL,15,F"You could have given me a heads up,
OL,16,Fyou've exposed me to Kimi now!"
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781518689
OL,3,CLewis Hamilton secures first Grand
OL,4,CPrix win for Ferrari in Barcelona
OL,6,FHe was assured all was fine and,
OL,7,Findeed, the Italian came in on lap 15
OL,8,Fas the order was maintained. Hamilton
OL,9,Fhad cut the gap to two seconds by
OL,10,Fstopping earlier but could not make
OL,11,Finroads to threaten Russell.
OL,13,FAntonelli was given permission to push
OL,14,Fin pursuit of the Ferrari driver and
OL,15,Fclosed to within a second before
OL,16,FHamilton pitted for a second time on
OL,17,Flap 28. Mercedes this time did not
OL,18,Freact.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781518689
OL,3,CLewis Hamilton secures first Grand
OL,4,CPrix win for Ferrari in Barcelona
OL,6,FThe Italian was soon haring after team-
OL,7,Fmate Russell, coming alive in the
OL,8,Fmiddle of the race although he
OL,9,Freceived a final warning for track
OL,10,Flimits on lap 30 ` less than half race
OL,11,Fdistance.
OL,13,FRussell fended off Antonelli into turn
OL,14,Fone and team principal Toto Wolff
OL,15,Fwould be forgiven for having nervous
OL,16,Fflashbacks to 10 years ago, when his
OL,17,Ftitle-tussling Mercedes drivers
OL,18,FHamilton and Nico Rosberg crashed each
OL,19,Fother out on this track.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781518689
OL,3,CLewis Hamilton secures first Grand
OL,4,CPrix win for Ferrari in Barcelona
OL,6,FHamilton knew he was in the fight for
OL,7,Fa record-extending 106th F1 win,
OL,8,Fasking his team what times he needed
OL,9,Fto deliver.
OL,11,FRussell and Norris made their second
OL,12,Fstop on lap 36 with Antonelli in a lap
OL,13,Flater, emerging just behind his team-
OL,14,Fmate but with the reigning world
OL,15,Fchampion now right on his tail.
OL,17,FHamilton now held the lead and was
OL,18,Ftold he had seven laps to his next
OL,19,Fstop. "This is the critical moment,
OL,20,Fgive everything, we have our chance,"
OL,21,Frace engineer Carlo Santi told him.
OL,26,@{D@GOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781518689
OL,3,CLewis Hamilton secures first Grand
OL,4,CPrix win for Ferrari in Barcelona
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThen came the moment. Fernando Alonso
OL,12,Fstopped on track on lap 41, triggering
OL,13,Fa virtual safety car and Ferrari
OL,14,Fpulled the trigger on pitting Hamilton.
OL,16,FIt was a gift for Hamilton, who came
OL,17,Fout with a two-second advantage. He
OL,18,Fwas noted for a yellow-flag
OL,19,Finfringement but soon cleared as he
OL,20,Fpulled away at the front in pursuit of
OL,21,Fthat long-awaited win.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781518689
OL,3,CLewis Hamilton secures first Grand
OL,4,CPrix win for Ferrari in Barcelona
OL,6,FNorris' race engineer said they
OL,7,Fexpected a penalty for Antonelli as
OL,8,Fthey reported him for exceeding track
OL,9,Flimits again. That did not come.
OL,11,FAntonelli overcame a fierce defence
OL,12,Ffrom team-mate Russell to take second
OL,13,Fon lap 61 before his engine gave way,
OL,14,Fblowing the title race wide open again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
